{"tid":232513,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟她是不是愛我","createTime":"2017-05-06T19:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T23:52:22.000Z","uid":20119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"925e31218fe3c60a631741daf28ac3f136f4a61f","tid":232513,"uid":20119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"今日有個女仔打電話給我， 話失戀，<br />\n想约我食飯唱K，去到後話買少少野，<br />\n根住問我借了錢買嘢，買完後，<br />\n而她不斷拉着我的手，我便與她說做我女朋友，<br />\n之後拖着手去吃反。<br />\n食反時佢話借咗前男友10幾萬，但未還，<br />\n而她和前男友分手要搬出來住，<br />\n所以需要買必需品 叫我幫她 <br />\n她帶我去馬沙幫她買3萬蚊coupon <br />\n又去manning買5萬蚊coupon <br />\n又問我借了6萬蚊 <br />\n佢話一定会還我 叫我信佢  <br />\n月尾会還我 仲話明天会打電話给我约出來 <br />\n我現在很害怕她会不会<br />\n騙錢定真的愛我 如果騙我我真是還不到"},{"pid":"25a07d6339f4c80e79f8d2446b3845ce1ad2ee6f","tid":232513,"uid":69421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"GG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b48b06c2f2996ca2d216b7d92dd502233bc7c6c","tid":232513,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"555f0f7ec47848acb7202d224b60332af8f1da47","tid":232513,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:12:08.000Z","msg":"你老豆呢"},{"pid":"c1ffe32e6353011347d91598e038ffd0bc63d6e4","tid":232513,"uid":20119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個問題一起解決"},{"pid":"278e63a7d2a4ff12a255e87f84e3bc3f79ef63bf","tid":232513,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:25:21.000Z","msg":"當然愛你<br />\n<br />\n唔愛你點會問你借錢?"},{"pid":"8e97a3c6eda3ee70e014d3e402db52b2bf18388f","tid":232513,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:56:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪你肯躝返去支那未"},{"pid":"c6103a192a2674c36b677e2bf9bc2a71ce6f6e12","tid":232513,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r